version_description: Correct Introduction and fingerstyle opening, Simple chords.
The other just isn't quite right. It sounds just off and isn't correct. I know this one is in the same format, but I feel it's a better representation of how the song sounds.
Tuned to the Album version, is in capo 2, has alternate intro tab, gives chord shapes for non-capo players
It's the correct chords from the acoustic version without capo.

This tab is based off of the chords used in the concert linked here (https://youtu.be/e0V6QAzdCnE?t=32m48s), where you can see the guitar chords pretty clearly. Remember that the guitar is in D tuning (whole step down).
